{"tid":1240463,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"明日大愚無人講！","createTime":"2019-06-18T10:48:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T21:16:52.000Z","uid":36927,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"77f37f20cd8d521a056b472625ce91bf9117dcbe","tid":1240463,"uid":36927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T10:48:32.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母<br />\n林奠依家急推明日大愚<br />\n趕住送錢比支那補血<br />\n真係當正我哋全香港市民係傻鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1萬億啊<br />\n派比全香港人嘅話可以一人拎14萬啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n14萬係咩概念？<br />\n係一個月入1萬2既打工仔一年人工<br />\n係4年半嘅生果金<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但啲人好似根本唔埋咁<br />\n要唔要出長輩圖引下啲廢老注意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f27ed2d5cac54f772205f6993f1f6e3abd3e18a","tid":1240463,"uid":36927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T10:49:31.000Z","msg":"仆佢個街啲錢我有份嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e40a0217e0f612b5f2c827dd865464cf03c76a2","tid":1240463,"uid":36927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T10:50:06.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母<br />\n送錢比維尼打貿易戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff5bc876f980b441a43e859b35072afab7fcd7e9","tid":1240463,"uid":36927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T10:50:53.000Z","msg":"冚佢個家鏟<br />\n下年又話無盈餘唔派錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bbc6bfdb21c838ee82020362be5151bd28bf18b","tid":1240463,"uid":65747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T10:51:28.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"846400881ff2c7f45519ae9c462d2a1f0bec0421","tid":1240463,"uid":36927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T10:51:47.000Z","msg":"唔可以幫支那補血<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9de4fbf41f37a451e263d32e1db14e0f307ae913","tid":12